latestPosts.caption:
FEF X Dharmatic Entertainment- Two Powerhouses one groundbreaking vision.

Last night, we witnessed history. Our stakeholders- from industry legends to Bollywood icons gathered to reveal a partnership that will reshape Indian startups. It is going to be a launchpad for aspiring entrepreneurs and startups.
.
In Frame:
Akshay Kumar: Investor & Mentor
Karan Johar: Investor & Promoter
Vagish Pathak: Chairman of FEF
Sandeep Jain: Director at Vega Industries Pvt. Ltd.
Ravi Jaipuria: Chairman of RJ Corp and the visionary behind Varun Beverages, Investor and Promoter at FEF
Manju Yagnik: Vice Chairperson at Nahar Group & Director at FEF
Sukhraj Nahar: Chairman and Managing Director at Nahar Group 
Apoorva Mehta: Dharmatic Entertainment CEO & Managing Director
Sanjay Nigam: Founder of FEF
Sonali Dugar: Executive Director at Dugar Finance & Investments Ltd & Director at FEF
.
